OL,3,CLondon surgeons save sight of
OL,4,CBangladeshi students injured in
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FSurgeons from a specialist London eye
OL,8,Fhospital have helped save the sight of
OL,9,Fmore than 20 Bangladeshi students who
OL,10,Fwere wounded in last summer's protests
OL,11,Fin the country.
OL,13,FMahi Muqit and Niaz Islam, consultant
OL,14,Fophthalmologists at Moorfields Eye
OL,15,FHospital in London, operated on more
OL,16,Fthan 100 patients during the visit to
OL,17,FDhaka last month.
OL,19,FThe pair evaluated 150 patients aged
OL,20,Fbetween 14 and 30 following the invite
OL,21,Fby Bangladesh's interim government.
