OL,7,FAll patients had suffered bullet
OL,8,Finjuries to the eyes after taking part
OL,9,Fin protests organised by Students
OL,10,FAgainst Discrimination in July, with
OL,11,Fthe majority receiving initial
OL,12,Ftreatment last year.
OL,14,FThe specialist surgeons then operated
OL,15,Fon 24 patients over two days to save
OL,16,Ftheir sight.
OL,18,FThose who did not have surgery were
OL,19,Fgiven a rehabilitation plan which was
OL,20,Fagreed with local doctors.
