OL,7,FMr Muqit, a senior vitreoretinal
OL,8,Fconsultant at Moorfields, said: "It
OL,9,Fwas an honour to be invited to help
OL,10,Fthese people, and an intense
OL,11,Fexperience for all of us.
OL,13,F"It's such a privilege to be able to
OL,14,Frestore sight to people who have lived
OL,15,Fwith sight loss for months."
OL,17,FSpeaking of one patient named Rohan,
OL,18,Fwho was operated on during the visit,
OL,19,FMr Muqit added: "He was with friends
OL,20,Fwhen he was shot in both eyes by the
OL,21,Fpolice.
