OL,7,F"He was blinded in both eyes, with one
OL,8,Fbeing beyond hope. Our operation on
OL,9,Fthe other eye fixed his retinal
OL,10,Fdetachment and removed scar tissue.
OL,12,F"We have every expectation that his
OL,13,Fvision will continue to improve as he
OL,14,Frecovers from the surgery.
