OL,7,FAnother patient named Romel had also
OL,8,Flost his vision, according to Mr
OL,9,FMuqit: "His surgery also repaired a
OL,10,Fretinal detachment after bullet
OL,11,Ftrauma, and he was also very pleased
OL,12,Fto hear that his vision will slowly
OL,13,Fimprove."
OL,15,FThe specialists also discovered that
OL,16,Fone 20-year-old patient, named Minhaj,
OL,17,Fstill had the original bullets inside
OL,18,Fhis eye from last July.
OL,20,FHe required complex surgery to remove
OL,21,Fthem and repair the damage.
