OL,4,CBangladeshi students injured in
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FAn estimated 1,000 people suffered
OL,8,Fsome form of eye trauma during the
OL,9,Fdemonstrations in July 2024.
OL,11,FAround 700 having emergency care from
OL,12,Fmedics at the National Institute of
OL,13,FOphthalmology and Hospital (NIOH) in
OL,14,FDhaka.
OL,16,FThe Moorfields specialists also
OL,17,Fprovided medical and surgical training
OL,18,Fto local doctors to bolster treatment
OL,19,Fservices at NIOH.
