OL,7,FMr Islam, a senior medical retina
OL,8,Fexpert at Moorfields, added: "I was
OL,9,Fdelighted to be able to share our
OL,10,Fexpertise and experience with
OL,11,Fcolleagues at NIOH ` we hope our
OL,12,Flegacy lies in having transferred
OL,13,Fskills to them, so they can in turn
OL,14,Foffer sight-saving surgery to many
OL,15,Fothers affected by eye trauma in
OL,16,FBangladesh."
